trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event is raised when an attempt to create a new user with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control fails.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError>사용 하 여 새 사용자를 만들 하려고 할 때 이벤트는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>실패를 제어 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError>

trans-unit.source: The CreateUserErrorEventArgs class provides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> property to indicate the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> enumeration value that corresponds to the error that occurred.
trans-unit.target: CreateUserErrorEventArgs 클래스를 제공는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A>나타내는 속성을는 <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus>발생 한 오류에 해당 하는 열거형 값입니다.</xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs"></xref> class.
A <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> object that describes the result of a <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser*> attempt.
Gets or sets a value indicating the result of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: 결과 나타내는 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: The CreateUserError property indicates the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> enumeration value that corresponds to the error that occurred during the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser> event.
trans-unit.target: CreateUserError 속성은 표시의 <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus>중에 발생 한 오류에 해당 하는 열거형 값의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser> </xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus>
